                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                                        <date>10 March 1846</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Revd. I. Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">My dear sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I am in receipt of your favor of 4th inst<lb/> but\n                                        have not yet received the package containing the<lb/>\n                                        occidents <sic>Pentiteuch</sic>. I shall be much pleased\n                                        to<lb/> keep the latter if it is bound to my laste[?] if not\n                                        I will<lb/> take another in its place. I am obliged for your\n                                        attention<lb/> in reccollecting[sic!] my desire for itâ€”where\n                                        ever you publish<lb/> an edition of the daily Holiday\n                                        prayers in a smaller<lb/> form than those now for Sale, you\n                                        will please put<lb/> me down for a set.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I will not forget to transmit to my brother in\n                                                  <placeName>China</placeName><lb/> your request\n                                        that he subscribes for the Occident.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I have within a few days received letters from\n                                                  <persName>Jacob<lb/></persName>\n                                        <persName>Abm. Joseph</persName>. The former will be here in\n                                        the course of<lb/> a few weeks.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(4)\">With regards to <persName>Hanford</persName> I\n                                        remain Dr sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(7)\">Yours Respy</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(7)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Isc. Moses Jr</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>I hope the \"Vidder\" is now happy</p>\n                              <p>I knew of her intended marriage when I was</p>\n                              <p>last in <placeName>Phila.</placeName> Has\n                                                  <persName>Wolfe</persName> yet gone?</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p39k46k08/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
